Titolo: Désiré (video game)

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: Désiré is a French indie point-and-click adventure video game by Sylvain Seccia published in 2016. The game is about the titular character, Désiré, an achromatic boy who only sees black and white, and the player guides him in 4 various parts of his life. The game contains themes such as sexuality, bullying, pedophilia, zoophilia, suicide, depression, morality,
feminism, BDSM and criticism of aspects of modern society such as capitalism and materialism.

Genere: Adventure 

Valutazione: N/A
